name: one of us
description:
#2
a continuation in my series of photos during my journey in Bantargebang, Indonesia. 

I was walking through the village beside the trash mountain, he was sitting there picking out the broken sandals, seems like he is sorting it by colours. His child is playing around him, running and laughing. Sometimes he picks up toys from the nearby trash pile to play with. He is one of the scavengers who live and work beside the trash mountain. One of many - KAB.98
